title: La Salle Powers Past St. Bonaventure, 3-0 (La Salle University Athletics)
text: ( Source : La Salle University Athletics ) ST. BONAVENTURE, N.Y. - The La Salle men's soccer team cruised to a 3-0 defeat of the St. Bonaventure Bonnies on Saturday night in Atlantic 10 action at Marra Athletics Fields Complex . Andrew Connors
